title: Daz3d - Bring Out Your Dead GM  G2M
description:
Details
"Bring out your dead! Bring out your dead!"

You have a village beset by the plague, a battlefield strewn with the fallen, or maybe an obnoxious brother-in-law who has worn out his welcome? This 3D pose set for Genesis and Genesis 2 Males will fit the bill neatly. The poses are designed to work with the Medieval cart for all your dead retrieval rendering needs. There is everything from piles of the dead (or dead zombies), to hauling away bodies (or moving the injured), to even sizing the Medieval cart down to human scale (and includes a pulling the cart pose, too!) A perfect collection of poses that'll have you saying "I'm not dead yet!"

As always, FeralFey poses are fact checked for gravity, balance, and realism.

What's Included and Features
Bring Out Your Dead Poses:
2 hierarchical pose presets for the Medieval Cart:
00 A Wagon to Size (to shrink the cart to human scale and tilt the cart for hauling purposes)
00 B Wagon to Default Size (returns the cart to its default size and position)
1 two-model vignette pose each for Genesis/Genesis 2 Males and the Medieval Cart:
01 A & B Pulling the Cart
5 three-person vignette poses each for Genesis/Genesis 2 Males:
03 A, B, & C Dead Body Pile 1
04 A, B, & C Dead Body Pile 2
05 A, B, & C Wagon Fodder
06 A, B, & C Dragging
07 A, B, & C Hauling
1 four-model vignette pose each for Genesis/Genesis 2 Males and the Medieval Cart:
02 A, B, C, & D Not Dead Yet
10 Scene Subset Presets each for Genesis/Genesis 2 Males and the Medieval Cart. Each includes a "vignette handle" for ease of use to move the vignette where you need it in your renders:
01 Pulling the Cart Front
02 Pulling the Cart Stage Right
03 Pulling the Cart Stage Left
04 Pulling the Cart Back
05 Not Dead Yet
06 Dead Body Pile 1
07 Dead Body Pile 2
08 Wagon Fodder
09 Dragging Body
10 Hauling Body
Notes
This product includes:
1 DSON Core Installer
1 Poser Companion Files Installer
